<div class="story">
<p>Sandy Ridge is a 28 lot sound to sea subdivision in Duck. The subdivision has an active homeowners association and an HOA fee to cover the private road maintenance, community pool upkeep and the ocean access and sound access. Sandy Ridge is located just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/ships-watch.asp" title="Ship's Watch">Ship's Watch</a> on the south and to the north is the <a href="http://frf.usace.army.mil/" title="Field Research Pier">Field Research Pier</a> for the Army Corp of Engineers. Being located next to the research pier offers some panoramic ocean and sound views over the expanse of vacant ocean front land.</p>
